        "client_msg_id": "a68a8b16-42d8-4335-9e2f-ca8163d185b9",
        "text": "Thanks for sharing <@UCUSW7WVD> :slightly_smiling_face: If anyone's curious, happy to chat through the process or like where this all came from.\n\nI've been spending a lot of time thinking about what kind of new roles might pop up if things keep progressing the way they have been. This series came about as I had started asking Claude to write some Sci Fi about a particular role we came up with in a chat and some of it ended up really good, so I decided I'd try to see how far I could push it and polish it up enough to feel good about publishing.",
