        "client_msg_id": "7c7f5862-8acb-4229-aed9-6f75d3ad7106",
        "text": "Living in a small city in a very heavily agricultural area, and having grown up in a small town — the small town, small-time farming, and serving people one knows personally in your story really resonated. Even here, though, small family farms aren't the norm anymore, I'm afraid.\n\nIn fact, if LLMs somehow could help us regain the \"smallness\" of technology rather than the big-tech we have today, I'd be a pretty big fan. Not sure I can share your optimism in good conscience, but I'm sure willing to strive for it!",
        "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "source_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_profile": {
            "avatar_hash": "e3e6bba2ae45",
